The delta file use case is the most nuanced point — the rolling overwrite behaviour (where Thursday's 5 records replace Wednesday's 1, and Friday's 1 replaces Thursday's 5) needs to be written up as a concrete use case document for the data team, as it's a non-trivial requirement.
